  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I've been working on an indie VR shooter game for a long time. The main game mode has 9 floors. The floors get progressively harder, and you can find unique weapons on each floor. Your ammunition is limited, and you need to focus on headshots to defeat enemies. There is also a zombie mode, a shooting range, and a carnival map where you can shoot targets and collect points.</p>",
